metadata.name: The Elderly Returning to the Mothership
metadata.description:
The photo was shot in Pula, on the seaside of Croatia.  While I was at the beach, I saw this scene of the elderly walking into the sea.
As if they were returning to the mothership, from whence they came. 
This double exposure was not done digitally in post. Instead, it was created at the moment of shooting, inside of the camera. 
The image used for double exposure is a composite of stitched and taped diapositives I found at the flea market. 
Shot with Cannon A1.
